Articles.Content:
Hello fellow KSP fans!

Join Ozzy, for a continuation of Ozzy's Interstellar Space Program, today as we try landing our rovers on Duna and Eve, and gather science from our probes! We're also going to continue our space station operations, and begin drilling for resources, in an attempt to set up a fueling station for our craft.

We'll be live @ 9:30am CST

http://www.twitch.tv/ozzyinspace

See you there!

Thanks!!

- Ozzy
